precis:
Amendment to the ATLANTIC REGIONAL SPECIAL SELECTIVE AND PROVISIONAL
ASSISTANCE REGULATIONS permitting a subsidy to be paid to reduce the costs
of moving silica sand from the quarry site to the mill where it is used
in the manufacture of glass and similar products.
